te>我係學生，讀緊書，返竹戈</blockquote><br />\n未打完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係學生，讀緊書，返的part time 人工都算係唔錯，明知自己呢一刻都夠錢洗，但總係好慳家。<br />\n有時係連食lunch錢都慳，是但係7仔買d野食/有時食個包（間唔中）就算，覺得自己好奇怪，成日連小小錢都唔想洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係7仔買 已經唔夠慳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb8d349cd562d91d730b20fce2ee262070ac9ccf","tid":111823,"uid":76791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主男定女</blockquote><br />\n有咩關係呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b7e80ce2cd764c98b8b622b5dfcdd9194faa8c","tid":111823,"uid":71826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:15:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主男定女</blockquote><br />\n有咩關係呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你再唔講個post就沉硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f006ca2a25373d6a8426772884412d0156e9b8e","tid":111823,"uid":70256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:15:27.000Z","msg":"平胸？"},{"pid":"92eede5201a4a571ac3deb77a0bcba7262220057","tid":111823,"uid":76791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慳錢係好事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀，不過連呢d婆仔數都要計，有時覺得自己好煩"},{"pid":"3b2e960d1a98ccdf587b7ea57fa1ed1ae25ddf02","tid":111823,"uid":70450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但無咁誇張<br />\n明明有錢 但只想日日食$20既頹飯<br />\nM記食個雞翼餐都唔係好捨得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9155fac0942875e83b70f2c1f2a26d2cfebfb1c9","tid":111823,"uid":65381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:26:39.000Z","msg":"我之前都會覺得洗錢好心痛<br />\n就算夠錢洗都會慳住<br />\n中學個陣阿媽比左訂飯錢<br />\n我會唔交 然後夜晚食飯個陣偷偷地喺自己個碗到&ldquo;不&rdquo;嘢食落食物盒到 <br />\n第二日lunch食<br />\n咁我就會覺得個個月都存到錢<br />\n跟住後尾朋友話我太慳<br />\n應該應洗即洗<br />\n我而家就抱住依種態度洗錢<br />\n例如食lunch唔會再咁計較洗多一蚊兩蚊<br />\n而係訂個合理範圍自己 40至50蚊內都係合理<br />\n但可能一個禮拜一兩日食40，50蚊<br />\n其餘日子食平啲"}]}